---
layout: base.njk
title: En Direct
description: "The live Forgotten Industries channel: shortform Bluesky dispatches and the local archive copy imported at build time."
permalink: /en-direct/index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">En Direct / live channel</p>
    <h1>En Direct</h1>
    <p class="tagline">{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="imported-signal-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="field-notes-heading">
      <p class="section-label">Imported Signal</p>
      <h2 id="imported-signal-heading">Latest dispatches from the live channel.</h2>
      <p class="entry-note">Newest first / imported from Bluesky at build time</p>
    </div>

    {% if fieldnotes.length %}
    <ol class="field-note-list en-direct-signal-list">
      {% for note in fieldnotes %}
      {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
      <li class="field-note-card">
        <header>
          <time datetime="{{ note.createdAt | isoDate }}">{{ note.createdAt | readableDate }}</time>
          <a href="{{ note.url }}" data-track="outbound-field-note">Source</a>
        </header>
        <p>{{ note.text | escape | nl2br | safe }}</p>
        <footer aria-label="Bluesky engagement">
          <span>{{ note.replyCount }} replies</span>
          <span>{{ note.repostCount }} reposts</span>
          <span>{{ note.likeCount }} likes</span>
        </footer>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
    {% else %}
    <div class="callout field-note-empty">
      <h3>Import Pending</h3>
      <p>No dispatches were available during this build. The live feed remains available on Bluesky.</p>
      <p class="action-row"><a href="{{ site.fieldNotesSubscribeUrl }}" data-track="outbound-bluesky">Open live Bluesky feed</a></p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    <p class="action-row"><a href="/field-notes/">Open all imported dispatches</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band" aria-labelledby="en-direct-lanes">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="field-notes-heading">
      <p class="section-label">Live Input</p>
      <h2 id="en-direct-lanes">One shortform signal. One archive copy.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="lane-list" aria-label="En Direct channels">
      <li>
        <a class="panel-link" href="#imported-signal-heading">
          <span>Live Dispatches</span>
          <h3>Imported Signal</h3>
          <p>The newest imported dispatches now land here. The complete archive remains available on-site.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="panel-link" href="{{ site.fieldNotesSubscribeUrl }}" data-track="outbound-bluesky">
          <span>Live Source</span>
          <h3>Bluesky</h3>
          <p>Open the external live feed for the newest field signal before the next site build imports it.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="panel-link" href="/posts/#atlas-reports">
          <span>ATLAS Reports</span>
          <h3>Moved to Le Signal</h3>
          <p>AI-assisted end-of-day summaries belong with the authored signal.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
